WORK IN PROGRESS

First, we have a hash of data.

We also have an ISSUU key and secret.

We take the hash, sort it and generate a params string.

We then generate a signature and add it to the params string.

We then prepend the url and go!


References

http://developers.issuu.com/api/
http://help.squarespace.com/guides/using-issuu-with-squarespace
